{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-one-img-js","path":"/art/machine/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"","html":"<p>我嘗試獨立搭建一個繪圖機器的原型，並完成第一幅以機器作為媒材的「自畫」像。作畫過程中，只要輸入一張圖片搭配一些預處理，機器就能將畫筆定位在指定的位置並繪製想要的圖案。技術上，用的是CNC三軸定位座標(2個步進馬達＋1個伺服馬達)，並搭配Gcode作為軟體控制。此外，在這些初步嘗試後，希望能讓機器對圖像有更深層的認知 (AI)，探索人類與機器共同協作的更多可能性。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Drawing machine","description":"I built a drawing machine which successfully painted my first self-portrait (test experiment)","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3953900709219857,"src":"/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/ca45b/machine.jpg","srcSet":"/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/01656/machine.jpg 125w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/8be41/machine.jpg 250w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/ca45b/machine.jpg 500w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/39525/machine.jpg 750w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/a0205/machine.jpg 1000w,\n/static/2b4362985201238961e3584aad3a7c90/2cac5/machine.jpg 3148w","sizes":"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px"}}}},"fields":{"slug":"/art/machine/"},"parent":{"birthTime":"2019-11-10T10:06:18.000Z","modifiedTime":"2019-12-25T14:03:51.533Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/art/machine/"}}}